{"tid":613654,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[吹水多過煎扒] 異國行街市加煎扒記","createTime":"2018-04-01T23:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T18:08:34.000Z","uid":63452,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a40583868a82702b54e179aa16e93a89fc320a","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"由於女友返左香港，得返我自己一個鳩fing fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n適逢今個禮拜放假，梗係出town 行下local 街市買餸煮餐好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行過肉檔就黎收檔，老闆娘見無啦啦有個華人 (我個城少華人) 就撩我傾計<br />\n傾完一輪入正題買牛扒，佢一賣賣一盤十鎊四大塊Sirloin ，佢八鎊賣左俾我<br />\n平時食開fillet steak 心思思想買, 佢又唔收我碎銀五鎊有兩細塊<br />\n結果十三鎊買左六塊扒走，抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下就係今餐會用到嘅嘢 (除左枝sunflower oil 唔記得左)<br />\n左下角材料有 (上排左至右，下排左至右):<br />\n牛油, Olive oil, 黑椒, 鹽, 乾parsley<br />\nThyme, garlic, sirloin, fillet steak<br />\n配菜方面就用前排買落嘅薯仔，用焗爐焗薯條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/073914_8d9ab92361828f773ee8b3fe6403d314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F073914_8d9ab92361828f773ee8b3fe6403d314.JPG&h=9569f4ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb45b14479cd0740dbecd5557266c9ab9bae5011","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我鍾意去街市買餸多過去超市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一黎街市野又新鮮又平<br />\n二黎比起對住部自動收銀機，係街市你可以同個檔主交流下<br />\n有咩想問e.g. 塊排點煎好，整薯條用咩薯仔好 直接問老細就得，佢地又會好奇你邊到黎，問下香港依家點，大家有傾有講不亦樂乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同啲老細熟左有時重會有得平或者有嘢送，試過係生果檔同老細吹緊水，佢見口乾無啦啦切個蘋果同我一人一半，成件事好warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有一單係講政治，不過容後再談，講返餐飯先"},{"pid":"b117c1ac4ef6b2509ef3547e65fa208de22ad975","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T23:48:55.000Z","msg":"首先preheat 定個爐250 度Celsius ，放埋個盤入去一齊加熱，記住唔駛落油！<br />\n再煲滾一煲水，加啲鹽加啲油<br />\n<br />\n洗乾淨薯仔，先沿長啲個方向切，再切做一條條1cm x 1cm 嘅薯條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/074716_ac866658d48cb7ea558c9345b529bcce.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F074716_ac866658d48cb7ea558c9345b529bcce.JPG&h=82456eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/074745_31f698c9282df60d8dae7aba019fd4c1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F074745_31f698c9282df60d8dae7aba019fd4c1.JPG&h=a3d5e93a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb7cdf70c742fceb1dd027472d361c6063a000bd","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T23:50:57.000Z","msg":"然後落薯條落滾水煮兩至三分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/074943_36f39ab95618faa2e869433b4c3f66d9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F074943_36f39ab95618faa2e869433b4c3f66d9.JPG&h=e52bf6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮好係sink 盤隔走啲水，先落油，再落鹽，黑椒同乾parsley，撈混<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075000_8dfdd0b6cc580200a309d9150e3e3673.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075000_8dfdd0b6cc580200a309d9150e3e3673.JPG&h=b49e1309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎個焗爐拎個盤出黎，倒啲薯條落去盡量隔開一條條 （會有jar jar 聲），放返入爐先焗十分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075024_2f0c181ae0328577696122cb54d2f0dd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075024_2f0c181ae0328577696122cb54d2f0dd.JPG&h=f8e514cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57b69343556d39d069829bb99f673669d9f23b12","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T23:54:43.000Z","msg":"就黎十分鐘，開始準備牛扒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛扒已經事先放係室溫半個鐘<br />\n印乾水，大量落鹽同黑椒，連側邊都唔好放過<br />\n熱定個pan ，我習慣用olive oil<br />\n為健康著想其實應該用high smoke point 嘅油 e.g. Sunflower oil but who cares? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075226_2a31593c7cbf3de92a677ad9ce8a3d43.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075226_2a31593c7cbf3de92a677ad9ce8a3d43.JPG&h=c74a0c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塊fillet 薄過塊sirloin 一半有多，我預每邊一分鐘就夠<br />\nSirloin 我第一次煎咁厚其實我無咩信心，我又無一個可以入焗爐嘅pan <del>(想買個skillet 但係女友唔俾)</del> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唯有每邊三分鐘<br />\n不過我食得生，rare 到medium rare 我都okay<br />\n調味方面，fillet steak 我打算簡簡單單鹽同黑椒就夠，sirloin 我就打算用gordon ramsay 式"},{"pid":"3cfb03fbdc77097d52c619c29eb90cf5ef59a081","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T23:57:51.000Z","msg":"薯條夠十分鐘，拎出黎，反轉佢，焗多十分鐘，同時開始剪牛扒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075544_d2a0e369893325966d7fbf290544978c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075544_d2a0e369893325966d7fbf290544978c.JPG&h=65ebe825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFillet 一分鐘反轉，個面有啲柒，可能未完全印乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075649_4cc4eb2a9b9a6ad4ce19c0a441892d3b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075649_4cc4eb2a9b9a6ad4ce19c0a441892d3b.JPG&h=6c452037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFillet 夠兩分鐘，拎起去rest<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075727_485ec1efbde530fdac96334837ef2f55.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075727_485ec1efbde530fdac96334837ef2f55.JPG&h=655f8acd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5da2dc3930b42daebcfea15d5bc34d274bb7d5d","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:02:11.000Z","msg":"Sirloin 夠三分鐘，反面，仆街好似太黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落thyme 同一舊拍左嘅garlic<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075919_aa10fd4bc07533430df3293fadfc3a6a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075919_aa10fd4bc07533430df3293fadfc3a6a.JPG&h=ff836103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊garlic 可以夾起抹塊扒，會上味好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/075949_383fef041f27aa3598b27cc97628facc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F075949_383fef041f27aa3598b27cc97628facc.JPG&h=57d037ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一分鐘落牛油，再淋上面，我諗睇得多牛扒post 嘅巴絲唔駛我教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/080034_814441fcf7d60a0004e95176ddb2c63c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F080034_814441fcf7d60a0004e95176ddb2c63c.JPG&h=835ca8c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煎埋舊肥，拎起，同塊fillet 一齊rest<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/080110_80d78541918c04b840e14e22280310fc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F080110_80d78541918c04b840e14e22280310fc.JPG&h=d4a5765f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8018710a5e26ae68249c7fd3676b5bdfbfc9e1c","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:04:54.000Z","msg":"Rest 完啲薯條都得了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/080325_4ead1db7b46d32326417b9b06bb57aa9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F080325_4ead1db7b46d32326417b9b06bb57aa9.JPG&h=ca43fb24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上碟, 落事先整落嘅garlic and herb butter<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/080340_b70e7e5e3b2deb0bed76233fe44918d6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F080340_b70e7e5e3b2deb0bed76233fe44918d6.JPG&h=4ee93edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ngarlic and herb butter 整法在此:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wUunZV3oIXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwUunZV3oIXA&d=OXD%2FC1mnfXajaQkMRDPQL%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1d5a1325\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wUunZV3oIXA</a>"},{"pid":"1a58534bf7f7d737a9ddaa1b9590f0117bcea474","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"究竟熟唔熟呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/080831_37c68cc6747cfcf53b769c5ad42f669f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F080831_37c68cc6747cfcf53b769c5ad42f669f.JPG&h=9f06e1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wQPM6nc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwQPM6nc.jpg&h=4615b6ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影落去好鮮紅，實際上fillet 偏medium rare, sirloin 偏rare<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩塊扒兩種食法，得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368d6ccdfdcde9fc5447526a44b62d0421500896","tid":613654,"uid":2536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"其實你食嗰陣會落garlic and herb butter 咁係咪就咁用鹽同胡椒粉煎就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ebbc4fc616920c9ea98c958d30ba826f24d36d","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"368d6ccdfdcde9fc5447526a44b62d0421500896","tid":613654,"uid":2536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"其實你食嗰陣會落garlic and herb butter 咁係咪就咁用鹽同胡椒粉煎就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:23:03.000Z","msg":"其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過牛油同thyme 落過鑊香啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1030deb24364096cacfcaab21b941ad3728c1ee","tid":613654,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab61327367c1967156e20417abd2f2613b179453","tid":613654,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1030deb24364096cacfcaab21b941ad3728c1ee","tid":613654,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:39:14.000Z","msg":"感謝推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281ba31c4b937184b79d4bd2960d2be2a0fbd54f","tid":613654,